feature_01_suppt_01_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_01_suppt_01_medium.value: From a rejuvenated Start menu, to new ways to connect to your favorite people, news, games, and content—Windows 11 is the place to think, express, and create in a natural way.[4]

feature_01_suppt_02_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_01_suppt_02_medium.value: NVIDIA® GeForce RTX™ 40 Series GPUs are beyond fast. Powered by the NVIDIA Ada Lovelace architecture which delivers a leap in both performance and AI-powered graphics. Experience lifelike virtual worlds with ray tracing and ultra-high FPS gaming.[5]

feature_01_suppt_03_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_01_suppt_03_medium.value: By synchronizing the refresh rates of your GPU and display, NVIDIA® G-SYNC™ technology delivers gameplay that’s sharp, fluid, and stutter-free with minimal input lag.

feature_01_suppt_04_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_01_suppt_04_medium.value: Reduce frustrating lag and image ghosting with a display that combines a 144 Hz refresh rate and a 1080p resolution for smooth, crisp gameplay.[6]

feature_01_suppt_05_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_01_suppt_05_medium.value: No matter where you stand, this screen delivers clear, vivid images with 178-degree wide-viewing angles, so everyone can get a great view.

feature_01_suppt_06_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_01_suppt_06_medium.value: Enjoy the sun and your favorite content with this anti-glare panel. Non-reflective and low gloss means you'll get less glare while you're outside.

feature_02_headline_04_statement.name: Feature headline
feature_02_headline_04_statement.value: Keyboard keycaps contain post-consumer recycled plastic

feature_02_suppt_01_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_02_suppt_01_medium.value: Using DC Dimming technology that controls brightness by adjusting direct current rather than cycling the backlight, we can eliminate screen flickering for more comfortable viewing.[7]

feature_02_suppt_02_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_02_suppt_02_medium.value: A 16:9 aspect ratio lets you see all of your game.

feature_02_suppt_03_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_02_suppt_03_medium.value: Built with the environment in mind, our laptop design includes sustainable materials like ocean-bound plastic in the speaker enclosure.[8]

feature_02_suppt_04_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_02_suppt_04_medium.value: We're bringing a more sustainable design to our keyboards by using keycaps made with post-consumer recycled plastic.[9]

feature_02_suppt_05_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_02_suppt_05_medium.value: This product meets at least 75% of the existing optional criteria to achieve EPEAT Gold registration.[10]

feature_02_suppt_06_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_02_suppt_06_medium.value: This product meets the criteria that require computers to operate efficiently to get ENERGY STAR certification.[10]

feature_03_suppt_01_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_03_suppt_01_medium.value: When your laptop is low on power, no one has time to wait hours to recharge. Power down your device and go from 0 to 50% charge in approximately 30 minutes.[11]

feature_03_suppt_02_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_03_suppt_02_medium.value: Enjoy faster speeds, improved performance, greater capacity and lower latencies than earlier iterations with Wi-Fi 6E and Bluetooth® 5.3 wireless card.[12]

feature_03_suppt_03_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_03_suppt_03_medium.value: Video chat in vibrant clarity with Full HD resolution, even in low light, and make every conversation a face-to-face experience for a better way to stay in touch.[13]

feature_03_suppt_04_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_03_suppt_04_medium.value: Plug in your external storage with this USB Type-A port, featuring 5Gbps signaling data rate.[14]

feature_03_suppt_05_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_03_suppt_05_medium.value: Free 12-month subscription of McAfee® LiveSafe™ service included. McAfee® LiveSafe™ service enriches your digital life by protecting your data, identity and all your devices so you can connect with confidence.[15]

feature_03_suppt_06_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_03_suppt_06_medium.value: Boot up in seconds with lightning fast speed with up to 512 GB PCIe SSD storage.

feature_04_suppt_01_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_04_suppt_01_medium.value: Take your audio experience to the next level with smart amplification technology giving you loud, clear and dynamic sound.

feature_04_suppt_02_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_04_suppt_02_medium.value: Pump up the volume to your favorite music, movie or game with dual-stereo speakers.

feature_04_suppt_03_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_04_suppt_03_medium.value: With dual channel technology, two channels work simultaneously to double the communication speed between the memory controller and the RAM increasing system performance.

feature_04_suppt_04_medium.name: Feature supporting point
feature_04_suppt_04_medium.value: This true multi-touch touchpad supports four finger gestures and lets you scroll, zoom, and navigate with a simple touch.

flex_value_prop_1_suppt.name: Flex value prop 1 supporting point
flex_value_prop_1_suppt.value: HP has included recycled content into over 95% of new PC’s and Displays since 2020.

ksp_01_suppt_01_long.name: Key selling point
ksp_01_suppt_01_long.value: Play at your best with a powerful Intel® Core™ Processor[1], a modern graphics card, and plenty of memory.

ksp_02_suppt_01_long.name: Key selling point
ksp_02_suppt_01_long.value: OMEN makes better performance easier with features that automatically optimize your gaming while you play.

ksp_03_suppt_01_long.name: Key selling point
ksp_03_suppt_01_long.value: Upgrade to a backlit keyboard and express your best gaming self.

ksp_04_suppt_01_long.name: Key selling point
ksp_04_suppt_01_long.value: EPEAT® Gold with Climate+[3] and ENERGY STAR® certified.

processorname.name: Processor
processorname.value: Intel® Core™ i7-14650HX (up to 5.2 GHz with Intel® Turbo Boost Technology, 30 MB L3 cache, 16 cores, 24 threads)[20,21]

proddes_overview_extended.name: Overview
proddes_overview_extended.value: The OMEN Laptop is made for peak PC gaming. This sleek machine touts a next generation Intel® Core™ Processor[1] and modern graphics card. This laptop also has new optimization features to push performance even further[2], updated thermals, and an upgraded keyboard.

proddes_overview_medium.name: Overview
proddes_overview_medium.value: Give your games the max graphics settings they yearn for with the latest Intel® Core™ Processors and NVIDIA® graphics.
